docs {
  ## Create Experiment - TTS (V1)

  Creates a TTS experiment. Models are object arrays with `name` + `config` (voice selection).
  model_params are keyed by base model name (not per-voice).
  output_format is "audio".

  ### Response
  ```json
  {"message": "Experiment created successfully.", "status": 200}
  ```
}
